name: code
description: * **data** contains the dataset in CSV or JSON format   * **sample.csv** contains an example dataset * **src** contains the CSS and JavaScript of your implementation   * **main_old.js** contains a small D3 example, which loads the CSV file and display it as a table   * **style.css** contains the styles for the visualization * **web_modules** contains external libraries (e.g., [D3](https://d3js.org)) * **index.html** entry point of the dashboard (see [below](#development-environment) how to run it)
